 background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></a>关于会员人数与发帖&amp;回复积极性的关系，三峡大学会员数量太多，几乎快是第二名两倍，我们排除三峡大学这个个例重新作图。</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1.25em; line-height: 1.25; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/nickliqian/Baidu-tieba-university#8会员人数活跃度排除最大值三峡大学\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" id=\"user-content-8会员人数活跃度排除最大值三峡大学\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(3, 102, 214); text-decoration-line: none; float: left; padding-right: 4px; margin-left: -20px; line-height: 1;\"></a>8.会员人数&amp;活跃度(排除最大值三峡大学)</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/nickliqian/Baidu-tieba-university/blob/master/Analysis%20Chart/%E4%BC%9A%E5%91%98%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0&%E6%B4%BB%E8%B7%83%E5%BA%A6(%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%80%BC%E4%B8%89%E5%B3%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6).png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(3, 102, 214); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/nickliqian/Baidu-tieba-university/raw/master/Analysis%20Chart/%E4%BC%9A%E5%91%98%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0&%E6%B4%BB%E8%B7%83%E5%BA%A6(%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%80%BC%E4%B8%89%E5%B3%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6).png\" alt=\"image\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></a>总的趋势是：&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/>1.主题帖/回复贴与会员人数成正比（除了北大清华三峡，会员众多，但很少发言）。&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/>2.人均发主题数量趋势较平稳，在0.5~1.5之间，中间段趋近于1（可以说具有一人一贴的特点，说明大部分人是有一定的需求（咨询，交流）后加入的贴吧）。&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/>3.人均回复贴数量集中在35条。&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/>4.每贴平均回复数量在会员人数超过5W后，曲线较为平稳，均值为每个主题帖约有27条回复（会员人数达到一定规模后，建立起社区生态）。&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1.25em; line-height: 1.25; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/nickliqian/Baidu-tieba-university#9会员人数与发言情况的散点图\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" id=\"user-content-9会员人数与发言情况的散点图\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(3, 102, 214); text-decoration-line: none; float: left; padding-right: 4px; margin-left: -20px; line-height: 1;\"></a>9.会员人数与发言情况的散点图</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/nickliqian/Baidu-tieba-university/blob/master/Analysis%20Chart/%E4%BC%9A%E5%91%98%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%91%E8%A8%80%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%95%A3%E7%82%B9%E5%9B%BE.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(3, 102, 214); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/nickliqian/Baidu-tieba-university/raw/master/Analysis%20Chart/%E4%BC%9A%E5%91%98%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%91%E8%A8%80%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%95%A3%E7%82%B9%E5%9B%BE.png\" alt=\"image\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></a><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1.25em; line-height: 1.25; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/nickliqian/Baidu-tieba-university#10主题吸引程度的散点图\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" id=\"user-content-10主题吸引程度的散点图\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(3, 102, 214); text-decoration-line: none; float: left; padding-right: 4px; margin-left: -20px; line-height: 1;\"></a>10.主题吸引程度的散点图</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/nickliqian/Baidu-tieba-university/blob/master/Analysis%20Chart/%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%95%A3%E7%82%B9%E5%9B%BE.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(3, 102, 214); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/nickliqian/Baidu-tieba-university/raw/master/Analysis%20Chart/%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%95%A3%E7%82%B9%E5%9B%BE.png\" alt=\"image\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></a>随着会员人均发主题帖数的增长，每个帖子的回复数是增长的，在人均发帖数达到1的时候，每个帖子回复数开始下降（水贴太多，不想回复）。</p><p><br/></p>','no mark','2017-10-01 04:40:56.775310','2017-10-07 06:36:05.370653',0,2,'项目采集各个普通本科大学贴吧的会员总数/发帖总数/回复总数/帖子标题/发帖时间。 思路：先从教育类网站获取本科大学名称，约1200个。 考虑到并不是所有大学贴吧都开放，依次以大学名称为关键词向百度贴吧发出请求，并设定条件验证大学贴吧是否建立，排除未建立的贴吧 整理后的贴吧数量约1000个，依次发出，并从响应中提取会员总数/发帖总数/回复总数等信息，写入本地数据库。 同时，提取每个贴吧前五页的帖子标');
